10-11-Motocross-Carmichael_N.htm | author = Perez AJ | title = Illness curtails Carmichael's motocross farewell | date = 2007-10-12 | accessdate = 2012-04-25 }}</ref> |[[Motocross]] racer |American |- |[[Cher]]<ref name="Lisman"/><ref name="autogenerated3">{{cite web |title=Interview with Cher |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/communicate/archive/cher/page3.shtml |publisher=BBC.co.uk |date=2006-11-05 |accessdate = 2007-10-16}}</ref> |Recording artist, actress, director, and record producer |American |- |[[Roger Cicero]] |Jazz and pop musician |German |- |[[Pema Chödrön]]<ref name="shambhala2010">{{cite web |url=http://www.shambhala.com/html/learn/features/pema/bio/index.cfm |author=Shambhala Publications |title=About Pema Chödrön |year=2010 }}</ref> |Buddhist nun |American |- |[[Tom Clarke (politician)|Tom Clarke]]<ref>{{cite news | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/health/341917.stm | title = MPs call for action on ME | accessdate = 2008-12-12 | date = 1999-05-12 | publisher = BBC }}</ref> |[[Politician]] |British |- |[[Neil Codling]]<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/80272/billboard-bits-fatboy-slim-suede-keb-mo | title = Billboard Bits: Fatboy Slim, Suede, Keb' Mo' | last = Cohen | first = J | date = 2001-03-23 | accessdate = 2008-12-09 | publisher = [[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]] }}</ref> |[[Keyboard instrument|keyboard]] player for the band [[Suede (band)|Suede]] |British |- |[[Michael Crawford]] |Actor and singer |British |- |[[Laura Dundovic]]<ref name="heraldsun1">{{cite web |url=http://www.heraldsun.com.au/ipad/tv-dating-host-battles-with-fatigue/story-fn6bn80a-1225957982634 |author=Herald Sun |title=TV dating host battles with fatigue |date=November 22, 2010 }}</ref> |Former [[Miss Universe Australia]] |Australian |- |[[Blake Edwards]]<ref name="Lisman"/><ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.businessweek.com/news/2010-12-16/blake-edwards-versatile-volatile-movie-director-dies-at-88.html |author= Harris K |title=Blake Edwards, Versatile, 