| 1516 || || [[Lê dynasty]] produces [[matchlocks]].{{sfn|Tran|2006|p=107}}
|-
| 1540 || || In [[Southeast Asia]] [[matchlocks]] start seeing widespread use.{{sfn|Andrade|2016|p=169}}
|}

